  "title": "大模型训练新突破！Meta 提出 LSP：无数据也能实现能力飞升",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652629311&idx=3&sn=bf5dabe2ce2bc1463bef5bf6ef48b324",
  "date": "2025-09-20 05:43:00",
